{"data":[{"date":"04:57 08/07","title":"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn, Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb \"troll\" v\u00ec l\u1ee1 d\u1ea1i \u0111\u1eb7t c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien.JPG","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Sau khi \u0110T Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Zlatan Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll b\u1edfi Rooney c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1edbi David Beckham.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/214818-3.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nC\u00e1c pha l\u00e0m b\u00e0n c\u1ee7a trung v\u1ec7 Harry Maguire v\u00e0 ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli \u0111\u00e3 gi\u00fap \u0110T Anh \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o ch\u01a1i \u1edf v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh, Zlatan Ibrahimovic v\u00e0 David Beckham c\u00f3 m\u00e0n \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u00fa v\u1ecb v\u1ec1 k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3. Ibrahimovic chia s\u1ebb tr\u00ean Twitter c\u00e1 nh\u00e2n d\u00f2ng \u0111\u00e1nh c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ea1i \u00fd: 'N\u1ebfu Anh th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd mua b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i \u1edf b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 n\u01a1i n\u00e0o anh mu\u1ed1n tr\u00ean th\u1ebf gi\u1edbi, nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng, anh mua cho t\u00f4i b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 th\u1ee9 g\u00ec t\u1eeb Ikea. OK?'<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll b\u1edfi Rooney v\u00e0 Beckham sau khi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll b\u1edfi Rooney v\u00e0 Beckham sau khi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thua h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/ibrahimovic-bi-troll-boi-rooney-va-beckham-sau-tran-thua-cua-thuy-dien.JPG\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Ibrahimovic b\u1ecb troll sau khi thua c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nZlatan Ibrahimovic v\u1ed1n l\u00e0 bi\u1ec3u t\u01b0\u1ee3ng c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0 Ikea l\u00e0 nh\u00e3n hi\u1ec7u \u0111\u1ed3 n\u1ed9i th\u1ea5t c\u00f3 xu\u1ea5t x\u1ee9 t\u1eeb \u0111\u1ea5t n\u01b0\u1edbc B\u1eafc \u00c2u n\u00e0y. Vi\u1ec7c Zlatan g\u1eedi l\u1eddi c\u00e1 c\u01b0\u1ee3c v\u1edbi Beckham khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi th\u00edch th\u00fa, b\u1edfi Becks c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t c\u1ef1u danh th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a b\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e1p l\u1ea1i, Beckham s\u1eeda ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng: 'N\u1ebfu Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i s\u1ebd \u0111\u00edch th\u00e2n \u0111\u01b0a anh \u0111\u1ebfn Ikea \u0111\u1ec3 mua b\u1ea5t c\u1ee9 m\u00f3n \u0111\u1ed3 n\u00e0o c\u1ea7n thi\u1ebft cho c\u0103n bi\u1ec7t th\u1ef1 m\u1edbi \u1edf LA. Nh\u01b0ng n\u1ebfu Anh gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n anh \u0111\u1ebfn xem m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh tr\u00ean s\u00e2n Wembley, nh\u1edb m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a Tam S\u01b0'.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ecb Anh lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 0-2, nhi\u1ec1u C\u0110V nhanh nh\u1ea3u \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ebf \u1ea3nh v\u1ec1 v\u1ee5 c\u01b0\u1ee3c n\u00e0y. M\u1ed9t C\u0110V c\u00f2n gh\u00e9p Ibrahimovic m\u1eb7c chi\u1ebfc \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ee7a \u0110T Anh nh\u01b0 l\u1eddi nh\u1eafc v\u1edbi c\u1ef1u tuy\u1ec3n th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Zlatan \u0111\u00e1p tr\u1ea3<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00e1m l\u00e0m d\u00e1m ch\u1ecbu, sau tr\u1eadn thua c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Ibrahimovic khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta ph\u1ea3i ph\u00ec c\u01b0\u1eddi khi \u0111\u0103ng t\u1ea3i tr\u00ean Twitter d\u00f2ng ch\u1eef: \"T\u00f4i \u0111\u1ebfn \u0111\u00e2y. Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng\". \u0110i\u1ec1u n\u00e0y khi\u1ebfn ng\u01b0\u1eddi ta li\u00ean t\u01b0\u1edfng \u0111\u1ebfn vi\u1ec7c Zlatan ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ea5p nh\u1eadn mua b\u1eefa t\u1ed1i cho Beckham, thay v\u00ec m\u1eb7c \u00e1o \u0111\u1ea5u c\u1ed5 v\u0169 cho \u0110T Anh.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong khi \u0111\u00f3, Wayne Rooney \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c th\u1ec3 tr\u00eau ch\u1ecdc Zlatan. Tr\u00ean Twitter, Rooney vi\u1ebft: 'C\u1ea3m th\u1ea5y th\u1ebf n\u00e0o h\u1ea3 Ibrahimovic. N\u1ebfu c\u1ea7n ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00e2m s\u1ef1, t\u00f4i lu\u00f4n \u1edf \u0111\u00e2y nh\u00e9\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Anh s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n Croatia \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/ghi-ban-ha-thuy-dien-alli-van-khong-hai-long-469-190651.html\">Ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ea1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Alli v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/huyen-thoai-mu-tuyen-anh-di-len-tu-tuyet-vong-thanh-tuyet-voi-421-190648.html\">Huy\u1ec1n tho\u1ea1i MU: Tuy\u1ec3n Anh \u0111i l\u00ean t\u1eeb tuy\u1ec7t v\u1ecdng th\u00e0nh tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi!</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/lot-vao-ban-ket-nguoi-anh-bat-dau-mo-cup-vang-421-190647.html\">L\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh b\u1eaft \u0111\u1ea7u m\u01a1 c\u00fap v\u00e0ng</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thua-tam-phuc-bai-tuong-cau-chuc-dt-anh-vo-dich-world-cup-2018-469-190645.html\">Thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c, b\u1ea1i t\u01b0\u1edbng c\u1ea7u ch\u00fac \u0110T Anh v\u00f4 \u0111\u1ecbch World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/hien-ngang-vao-ban-ket-kane-tuyen-bo-khong-ngai-doi-thu-nao-469-190644.html\">Hi\u00ean ngang v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Kane tuy\u00ean b\u1ed1 kh\u00f4ng ng\u1ea1i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 n\u00e0o</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong><br type=\"_moz\">\r\n</strong></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1012","checkdouble":"190650"},{"date":"04:48 08/07","title":"Ghi b\u00e0n h\u1ea1 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n, Alli v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/7/ghi-ban-ha-thuy-dien-alli-van-khong-hai-long.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Ti\u1ec1n v\u1ec7 Dele Alli kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng v\u1edbi m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n c\u1ee7a ch\u00ednh m\u00ecnh tr\u01b0\u1edbc Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n d\u00f9 anh \u0111\u00e3 ghi b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 cho Tam S\u01b0.</h2><h2>Alli ghi b\u00e0n quan tr\u1ecdng cho Tam S\u01b0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\" target=\"_blank\">tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Anh v\u00e0 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n</span>, v\u1ecb tr\u00ed c\u1ee7a Dele Alli b\u1ecb b\u00e0n t\u00e1n kh\u00e1 nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u01b0ng HLV Southgate quy\u1ebft \u0111\u1ecbnh gi\u1eef nguy\u00ean ng\u00f4i sao c\u1ee7a Tottenham trong \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh xu\u1ea5t ph\u00e1t \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u1ed1i \u0111\u1ea7u v\u1edbi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ea1i Samara.<br>\r\n<br>\r\nSau khi kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o ra b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 d\u1ea5u \u1ea5n n\u00e0o trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t, ng\u00f4i sao 22 tu\u1ed5i \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u ghi b\u00e0n sau pha t\u1ea1t b\u00f3ng chu\u1ea9n x\u00e1c c\u1ee7a Jesse Lingard. \u0110\u00f3 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n \u1ea5n \u0111\u1ecbnh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng 2-0 \u0111\u1ec3 \u0111\u01b0a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean t\u1eeb n\u0103m 1990.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2>Alli v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh Ghi b\u00e0n quan tr\u1ecdng, Alli v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh Ghi b\u00e0n quan tr\u1ecdng, Alli v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng h\u00e0i l\u00f2ng h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/7/ghi-ban-ha-thuy-dien-alli-van-khong-hai-long.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Alli ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf tr\u1eadn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">M\u1eb7c d\u00f9 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u00f3 \u00fd ngh\u0129a c\u1ef1c k\u1ef3 quan tr\u1ecdng v\u00e0 c\u0169ng l\u00e0 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng th\u00f4ng n\u00f2ng \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay nh\u01b0ng Alli v\u1eabn kh\u00f4ng m\u1ea5y vui v\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u. Alli cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00e1ng l\u1ebd ra anh c\u00f3 th\u1ec3 t\u1ea1o t\u1ea7m \u1ea3nh h\u01b0\u1edfng l\u1edbn h\u01a1n nhi\u1ec1u t\u1edbi tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<em>\u201cC\u1ea3m gi\u00e1c ghi b\u00e0n lu\u00f4n tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t l\u00e0 \u1edf m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u quan tr\u1ecdng nh\u01b0 v\u1eeba qua. Nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng cho r\u1eb1ng \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a m\u00ecnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cTr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua qu\u1ea3 th\u1ef1c r\u1ea5t kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n. \u0110i\u1ec1u quan tr\u1ecdng l\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 ni\u1ec1m tin v\u00e0o k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch t\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 c\u00e1ch m\u00e0 ch\u00fang t\u00f4i mu\u1ed1n ch\u01a1i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ki\u1ec3m so\u00e1t b\u00f3ng v\u01b0\u1ee3t tr\u1ed9i nh\u01b0ng c\u0169ng r\u1ea5t ki\u00ean nh\u1eabn. Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng t\u1eebng ch\u1ee9ng t\u1ecf h\u1ecd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 v\u00f4 c\u00f9ng kh\u00f3 ch\u01a1i \u1edf c\u00e1c tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n\u201cT\u00f4i ngh\u0129 \u0111\u00e2y l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t th\u00e0nh t\u00edch tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi v\u1edbi to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i r\u1ea5t vui khi nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 c\u1ed5 v\u0169 c\u1ee7a m\u1ecdi ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u1eeb kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i cho t\u1edbi qu\u00ea nh\u00e0. Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n tr\u00ecnh di\u1ec5n t\u1ed1t c\u1ee7a to\u00e0n \u0111\u1ed9i\u201d.</em><br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Anh vs Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n:</strong><br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1011","checkdouble":"190651"},{"date":"05:09 08/07","title":"Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Zlatko Dalic c\u1ee7a Croatia cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/993516564.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, video highlights t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Croatia t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Nga vs Croatia<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn cho su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn\" - HLV Zlatko Dalic chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Croatia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Croatia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-noi-ve-tran-dau-voi-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Croatia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u x\u00fac c\u1ea3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Nga v\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f9ng tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i th\u00eam hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, r\u1ed3i lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3o nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Croatia m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-3 (2-2 trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u) \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac kh\u00f3 n\u00e9n<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, HLV Zlatko Dalic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng: \"T\u00f4i c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Rakitic, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00f4i m\u1edbi nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Croatia c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac pha tr\u1ed9n trong t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hay kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3c, b\u1edfi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Croatia vao ban ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"\u0110T Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/ban-ket-wc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ea3i qua hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, \u0110T Croatia g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c khi g\u1eb7p Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Tam S\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb trung v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eadt hay. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-chien-sieu-kich-tinh-nga-vs-croatia-469-190656.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-croatia-465-190653.html\">HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-croatia-421-190640.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Croatia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-croatia-463-190636.html\">Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (KT): G\u1ea5u Nga t\u1eeb thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nga-vs-croatia-1h00-ngay-87-co-hoi-nao-cho-chu-nha-462-190583.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1010","checkdouble":"190652"},{"date":"05:24 08/07","title":"HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: \"Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Cherchesov n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o khi ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu g\u1ee5c ng\u00e3 tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u may r\u1ee7i \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/993516564.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, video highlights t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Croatia t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u01b0\u1edbc gi\u1ea3i, ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 Nga l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 v\u1ecb tr\u00ed th\u1ea5p nh\u1ea5t \u1edf BXH FIFA trong s\u1ed1 32 \u0111\u1ed9i g\u00f3p m\u1eb7t t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018. Tuy nhi\u00ean, \u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 g\u00e2y \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng m\u1ea1nh khi \u0111\u00e1nh b\u1ea1i Saudi Arabia v\u00e0 Ai C\u1eadp v\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1eadm, th\u1eadm ch\u00ed lo\u1ea1i c\u1ea3 T\u00e2y Ban Nha \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<div style=\"width: 100%;\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nga n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Nga n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/HLV-Nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Nga \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 m\u1ed9t k\u1ef3 World Cup \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1edb.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTrong tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft v\u1edbi Croatia, \u0110T Nga m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 v\u1edbi c\u00fa s\u00fat \u0111\u1eb9p m\u1eaft c\u1ee7a Cheryshev. Ngay c\u1ea3 khi b\u1ecb d\u1eabn b\u00e0n trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, Mario Fernandes v\u1eabn cho th\u1ea5y s\u1ef1 ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng c\u1ee7a \u0110T Nga v\u1edbi b\u00e0n g\u1ee1 h\u00f2a 2-2. Qua \u0111\u00f3 k\u00e9o Croatia v\u00e0o lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tuy nhi\u00ean,\u00a0 Fedor Smolov v\u00e0 ch\u00ednh Mario Fernandes \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ef1c hi\u1ec7n kh\u00f4ng th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng c\u00fa s\u00fat 11 m\u00e9t. Th\u1ea5t b\u1ea1i 3-4 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Croatia tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u khi\u1ebfn \u0110T Nga ph\u1ea3i d\u1eebng b\u01b0\u1edbc \u1edf v\u00f2ng t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 b\u1ea1i tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng HLV Nga n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i ch\u1ec9 c\u1ed1 g\u1eafng c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb b\u1ea3n th\u00e2n b\u1eb1ng c\u00e1ch l\u00e0m vi\u1ec7c ch\u0103m ch\u1ec9. T\u00f4i tin r\u1eb1ng moi ng\u01b0\u1eddi ban \u0111\u1ea7u kh\u00f4ng th\u1ef1c s\u1ef1 tin v\u00e0o \u0110T Nga\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Nga noi ve tran thua Croatia voi su tu hao.\" title=\"HLV Nga n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-croatia.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Nga n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn thua Croatia v\u1edbi s\u1ef1 t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n\"Nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd th\u00ec ai c\u0169ng y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. C\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd bi\u1ebft gi\u00e1 tr\u1ecb c\u1ee7a c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga. Hy v\u1ecdng ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd gi\u00fap c\u1ea3i thi\u1ec7n t\u00ecnh h\u00ecnh t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">B\u1ecb lo\u1ea1i kh\u1ecfi World Cup 2018 nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Nga v\u1eabn \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng khi gi\u1edbi thi\u1ec7u nhi\u1ec1u nh\u00e2n t\u1ed1 n\u1ed5i b\u1eadt. C\u00f2n Croatia s\u1ebd ch\u1ea1m tr\u00e1n \u0110T Anh t\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Nga t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-croatia-421-190640.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Croatia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-croatia-463-190636.html\">Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (KT): G\u1ea5u Nga t\u1eeb thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-vat/mario-fernandes-chang-hau-ve-dac-biet-chang-the-hat-quoc-ca-nga-389-190623.html\">Mario Fernandes: Ch\u00e0ng h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 \u0111\u1eb7c bi\u1ec7t ch\u1eb3ng th\u1ec3 h\u00e1t Qu\u1ed1c Ca Nga</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nga-vs-croatia-1h00-ngay-87-co-hoi-nao-cho-chu-nha-462-190583.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/world-cup-2018-chiec-giay-vang-goi-ten-ai-421-190348.html\">C\u1eadp nh\u1eadt danh s\u00e1ch c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018: Chi\u1ebfc gi\u00e0y v\u00e0ng g\u1ecdi t\u00ean ai?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1009","checkdouble":"190653"},{"date":"05:15 08/07","title":"3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n thua \u0111\u1eafng \u0110T Anh","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/3-ly-do-khien-thuy-dien-thua-dang-dt-anh.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>\u0110\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u00e3 thua t\u00e2m ph\u1ee5c kh\u1ea9u ph\u1ee5c Anh trong ng\u00e0y m\u00e0 c\u00e1c tuy\u1ebfn c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd \u0111\u1ec1u ch\u01a1i kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. C\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua 3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Janne Andersson th\u1eadm ch\u00ed c\u00f2n kh\u00f4ng ghi n\u1ed5i m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc Tam S\u01b0.</h2><h2>Chi\u1ebfn thu\u1eadt ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 y\u1ebfu k\u00e9m\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Viking thua \u0111\u1eafng Tam S\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh 3 l\u00fd do khi\u1ebfn Viking thua \u0111\u1eafng Tam S\u01b0 h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Thuy-Dien-vs-Anh-3-ly-do-khien-Viking-thua-dang-Tam-Su-hinh-anh.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n b\u1ecb \u0111\u1eadp tan sau m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3nh kh\u1eafc l\u01a1 l\u00e0</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ed1t cho t\u1edbi ph\u00fat 30 c\u1ee7a tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, th\u1eddi \u0111i\u1ec3m h\u1ecd th\u1ee7ng l\u01b0\u1edbi b\u00e0n thua \u0111\u1ea7u ti\u00ean. \u0110\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng B\u1eafc \u00c2u ph\u00e2n c\u00f4ng k\u00e8m ng\u01b0\u1eddi kh\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t khi \u0111\u1ec3 Forsberg \u0111eo b\u00e1m Maguire. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh d\u1ec5 d\u00e0ng ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u00e0n th\u1eafng v\u00e0o l\u01b0\u1edbi Olsen v\u1edbi m\u1ed9t c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u m\u1ea1nh nh\u01b0 b\u00faa b\u1ed5.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Alli sau \u0111\u00f3 kho\u1ea3ng 30 ph\u00fat c\u0169ng l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t sai l\u1ea7m c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng \u00e1o v\u00e0ng gi\u0103ng b\u1eaby vi\u1ec7t v\u1ecb qu\u00e1 k\u00e9m khi \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt m\u1ea5t m\u1ed9t c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 b\u0103ng xu\u1ed1ng. \u1ede m\u1ed9t kho\u1ea3ng c\u00e1ch thu\u1eadn l\u1ee3i v\u00e0 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u trong t\u01b0 th\u1ebf kh\u00f4ng ng\u01b0\u1eddi k\u00e8m, Alli \u0111\u00e3 n\u1eafm l\u1ea5y c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ghi b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng c\u1ea3 hai tay.</div>\r\n<h2>Thi\u1ebfu s\u1ef1 ph\u1ee5c v\u1ee5 cho c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Walker\" title=\"Walker\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/051035-2.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft treo b\u00f3ng c\u1ea7u may v\u00e0o v\u00f2ng c\u1ea5m \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00e1c chi\u1ebfn binh Viking g\u1ea7n nh\u01b0 kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ti\u1ebfp c\u1eadn khung th\u00e0nh trong hi\u1ec7p m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn <span href=\"https://bongda24h.vn/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\" target=\"_blank\">Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh</span> v\u1eeba qua. H\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng nh\u1eadn \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c l\u1eddi khen nh\u01b0ng r\u00f5 r\u00e0ng nh\u1eefng c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u0169ng c\u00f3 l\u1ed7i kh\u00f4ng nh\u1ecf khi t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng qu\u00e1 t\u1ec7.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nB\u1ed9 \u0111\u00f4i h\u1eadu v\u1ec7 c\u00e1nh Augustinsson v\u00e0 Krafth ch\u1ec9 bi\u1ebft t\u1ea1t c\u1ea7u may. Nh\u1edd v\u1eady, ba trung v\u1ec7 c\u1ee7a Anh gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft nh\u1eefng pha b\u00f3ng n\u00e0y kh\u00e1 g\u1ecdn g\u00e0ng. \u1ede gi\u1eefa s\u00e2n, Jordan Henderson c\u00e0ng \u0111\u1ea3m b\u1ea3o s\u1ef1 ch\u1eafc ch\u1eafn h\u01a1n cho Tam S\u01b0 khi c\u1eaft \u0111\u1ee9t h\u1ea7u h\u1ebft m\u1ecdi \u0111\u1ee3t t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng h\u1ee9a h\u1eb9n c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1eeb trong tr\u1ee9ng n\u01b0\u1edbc.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u0110i\u1ec1u \u0111\u00f3 khi\u1ebfn cho hai ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Marcus Berg v\u00e0 Ola Toivonen c\u1ee7a Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n kh\u00f4ng c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u b\u00f3ng \u0111\u1ec3 ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p t\u1ea5n c\u00f4ng c\u00f9ng nhau. Ch\u01b0a k\u1ec3, kh\u1ea3 n\u0103ng tri\u1ec3n khai b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a &ldquo;Viking&rdquo; l\u00e0 kh\u00e1 ch\u1eadm ch\u1ea1p v\u00e0 thi\u1ebfu t\u00ednh s\u00e1ng t\u1ea1o. Do v\u1eady, c\u00e1c ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd c\u00e0ng b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ea9y v\u00e0o th\u1ebf c\u00f4 l\u1eadp h\u01a1n v\u00e0 kh\u00f3 t\u1ea1o \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i ngon \u0103n \u0111\u1ec3 ghi b\u00e0n.</div>\r\n<h2>Pickford qu\u00e1 xu\u1ea5t s\u1eafc\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Pickford\" title=\"Pickford\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/051138-3.jpg\" /></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Pickford c\u1ee9u thua xu\u1ea5t th\u1ea7n cho \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">C\u00f3 th\u1ec3 n\u00f3i, Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n v\u00e0o tr\u1eadn v\u1edbi t\u00e2m th\u1ebf c\u1ea7m h\u00f2a Tam S\u01b0 b\u1eb1ng m\u1ecdi gi\u00e1. Ch\u00ednh v\u00ec v\u1eady, khi ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn b\u00e0n thua tr\u01b0\u1edbc, \u0111o\u00e0n qu\u00e2n c\u1ee7a HLV Andersson \u0111\u00e3 \u1edf v\u00e0o th\u1ebf b\u1ecb \u0111\u1ed9ng v\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng bi\u1ebft ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0m g\u00ec \u0111\u1ec3 t\u00ecm ki\u1ebfm b\u00e0n g\u1ee1.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNh\u01b0ng sau gi\u1edd ngh\u1ec9, \u0111\u1ea1i di\u1ec7n c\u1ee7a B\u1eafc \u00c2u ch\u01a1i m\u01b0\u1ee3t h\u01a1n r\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u. Nh\u1eefng pha ph\u1ed1i h\u1ee3p c\u1ee7a h\u1ecd tr\u1edf n\u00ean b\u00e0i b\u1ea3n h\u01a1n v\u00e0 nh\u1eefng c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i \u0103n b\u00e0n r\u00f5 r\u1ec7t c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c t\u1ea1o ra. C\u00f3 \u0111i\u1ec1u, m\u1ed7i khi h\u00e0ng ph\u00f2ng ng\u1ef1 c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh b\u1ecb ph\u00e1 h\u1ecfng, Jordan Pickford v\u1eabn c\u00f3 m\u1eb7t \u0111\u00fang l\u00fac \u0111\u1ec3 s\u1eeda sai cho c\u00e1c \u0111\u1ed3ng \u0111\u1ed9i.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n\u1ede tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 t\u1ea1o ra 3 pha c\u1ee9u thua th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u. \u0110\u1ea7u ti\u00ean l\u00e0 pha bay ng\u01b0\u1eddi h\u1ebft c\u1ee1 \u0111\u1ec3 c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u c\u1ee7a Marcus Berg ngay \u0111\u1ea7u hi\u1ec7p hai. Sau \u0111\u00f3 ti\u1ebfp t\u1ee5c l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ee9u thua th\u1ea7n s\u1ea7u khi Claesson c\u00f3 c\u01a1 h\u1ed9i s\u00fat c\u1eadn th\u00e0nh khi Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n t\u1ed5 ch\u1ee9c ph\u1ea3n c\u00f4ng t\u1ed1t. Cu\u1ed1i c\u00f9ng l\u00e0 pha c\u1ea3n ph\u00e1 b\u1eb1ng nh\u1eefng \u0111\u1ea7u ng\u00f3n tay cu\u1ed1i tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ec3 ng\u0103n Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n c\u00f3 \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c d\u00f9 ch\u1ec9 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t b\u00e0n danh d\u1ef1.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nV\u1edbi chi\u1ebfn c\u00f4ng v\u1eeba qua, Pickford \u0111\u00e3 tr\u1edf th\u00e0nh th\u1ee7 m\u00f4n tr\u1ebb nh\u1ea5t trong l\u1ecbch s\u1eed \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh gi\u1eef s\u1ea1ch l\u01b0\u1edbi trong m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u \u1edf World Cup. V\u00e0 \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t ph\u1ea7n th\u01b0\u1edfng x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng v\u1edbi nh\u1eefng g\u00ec m\u00e0 anh \u0111\u00e3 th\u1ec3 hi\u1ec7n xuy\u00ean su\u1ed1t gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u l\u1ea7n n\u00e0y.<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n vs Anh:</strong><br />\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/thay-gi-trong-ngay-anh-tro-lai-ban-ket-world-cup-sau-gan-ba-thap-ky-421-190646.html\">Th\u1ea5y g\u00ec trong ng\u00e0y Anh tr\u1edf l\u1ea1i b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup sau g\u1ea7n ba th\u1eadp k\u1ef7?</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-anh-vs-thuy-dien-461-190635.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n 0-2 Anh (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Xu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1008","checkdouble":"190654"},{"date":"05:43 08/07","title":"HLV Zlatko Dalic: \"Nga vs Croatia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p\"","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-noi-ve-tran-dau-voi-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>HLV Zlatko Dalic c\u1ee7a Croatia cho r\u1eb1ng tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga kh\u00f4ng h\u1ec1 \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n \u0111\u00f3 l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn v\u00e0 th\u1eeba nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ed9i b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a \u00f4ng \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn h\u01a1n \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7.</h2><div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/993516564.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, video highlights t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Croatia t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Cu\u1ed9c chi\u1ebfn gi\u1eefa Nga vs Croatia<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Ch\u00fac m\u1eebng c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u1ee7a t\u00f4i c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Nga, nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u0111\u00e3 chi\u1ebfn \u0111\u1ea5u r\u1ea5t qu\u1ea3 c\u1ea3m. \u0110\u00e2y kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p, \u0111\u01a1n gi\u1ea3n l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn, m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn cho su\u1ea5t v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 may m\u1eafn\" - HLV Zlatko Dalic chia s\u1ebb sau tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"HLV Croatia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"HLV Croatia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/hlv-croatia-noi-ve-tran-dau-voi-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>HLV Croatia n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Nga v\u1edbi nhi\u1ec1u x\u00fac c\u1ea3m sau chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nC\u1ea3 Nga v\u00e0 Croatia c\u00f9ng tr\u1ea3i qua nh\u1eefng gi\u00e2y ph\u00fat kh\u00f3 kh\u0103n \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft. Tr\u01b0\u1edbc \u0111\u00f3 \u1edf v\u00f2ng 1/8, hai \u0111\u1ed9i \u0111\u1ec1u ph\u1ea3i gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 \u0111i ti\u1ebfp tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u n\u00ean vi\u1ec7c ph\u1ea3i ch\u01a1i th\u00eam hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5, r\u1ed3i lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u l\u00e0 kh\u1ea3o nghi\u1ec7m v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u00fd ch\u00ed c\u1ee7a c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 hai \u0111\u1ed9i.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Croatia m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u v\u1edbi t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 4-3 (2-2 trong th\u1eddi gian thi \u0111\u1ea5u) \u0111\u1ec3 gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Nh\u1eefng c\u1ea3m x\u00fac kh\u00f3 n\u00e9n<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Sau khi gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, HLV Zlatko Dalic kh\u00f4ng th\u1ec3 gi\u1ea5u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c s\u1ef1 x\u00fac \u0111\u1ed9ng: \"T\u00f4i c\u0103ng c\u1ee9ng trong c\u1ea3 tr\u1eadn nh\u01b0ng sau c\u00fa \u0111\u00e1 c\u1ee7a Rakitic, c\u1ea3 ng\u01b0\u1eddi t\u00f4i m\u1edbi nh\u1eb9 nh\u00f5m \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c. Kh\u00f4ng ch\u1ec9 \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n m\u00e0 c\u1ea3 nh\u1eefng ng\u01b0\u1eddi \u1edf Croatia c\u0169ng th\u1ea5y h\u1ea1nh ph\u00fac\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"R\u1ea5t nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea3m x\u00fac pha tr\u1ed9n trong t\u00f4i. T\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng hay kh\u00f3c nh\u01b0ng gi\u1edd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t l\u00fd do t\u1ed1t \u0111\u1ec3 kh\u00f3c, b\u1edfi Croatia \u0111\u00e3 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. \u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 th\u00e0nh c\u00f4ng tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi, m\u1ed9t k\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 tuy\u1ec7t v\u1eddi\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Croatia vao ban ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"\u0110T Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/ban-ket-wc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nTr\u1ea3i qua hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u1ea3i ph\u00e2n \u0111\u1ecbnh th\u1eafng thua tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u, \u0110T Croatia g\u1eb7p b\u1ea5t l\u1ee3i v\u1ec1 th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c khi g\u1eb7p Anh \u1edf b\u00e1n k\u1ebft. Ngo\u00e0i ra, Tam S\u01b0 c\u0169ng \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 cao h\u01a1n nh\u1edd s\u1edf h\u1eefu \u0111\u1ed9i h\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb trung v\u1edbi \u0111\u1ed9 tu\u1ed5i trung b\u00ecnh tr\u1ebb th\u1ee9 hai t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">D\u00f9 v\u1eady, HLV Dalic kh\u1eb3ng \u0111\u1ecbnh: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i kh\u00f4ng mu\u1ed1n d\u1eebng l\u1ea1i v\u00e0 s\u1ebd c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ec3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn th\u1eadt hay. V\u1eabn c\u00f2n hai tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u ph\u00eda tr\u01b0\u1edbc n\u00ean c\u1ea3 \u0111\u1ed9i c\u00f3 nhi\u1ec1u \u0111\u1ed9ng l\u1ef1c. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i s\u1ebd l\u00e0m m\u1ecdi th\u1ee9 c\u00f3 th\u1ec3. \u0110\u00f3 s\u1ebd l\u00e0 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn kh\u00e1c nh\u01b0ng t\u00f4i tin v\u00e0o t\u1eadp th\u1ec3 n\u00e0y\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7.</div>\r\n<h2>Xem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-chien-sieu-kich-tinh-nga-vs-croatia-469-190656.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-croatia-465-190653.html\">HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-croatia-421-190640.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Croatia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-croatia-463-190636.html\">Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (KT): G\u1ea5u Nga t\u1eeb thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/nhan-dinh-world-cup-2018/nhan-dinh-nga-vs-croatia-1h00-ngay-87-co-hoi-nao-cho-chu-nha-462-190583.html\">Nh\u1eadn \u0111\u1ecbnh Nga vs Croatia (1h00 ng\u00e0y 8/7): C\u01a1 h\u1ed9i n\u00e0o cho ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0?</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1007","checkdouble":"190655"},{"date":"05:28 08/07","title":"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-chien-sieu-kich-tinh-nga-vs-croatia.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Nga vs Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 t\u1ea1i s\u00e2n Fisht m\u1ed9t m\u00e0n r\u01b0\u1ee3t \u0111u\u1ed5i t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 nh\u01b0 phim h\u00e0nh \u0111\u1ed9ng. Chung cu\u1ed9c, Croatia l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng sau lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u nh\u1edd m\u1eafc \u00edt sai l\u1ea7m h\u01a1n. H\u00e3y c\u00f9ng \u0111i\u1ec3m qua nh\u1eefng th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u0111\u00e1ng ch\u00fa \u00fd nh\u1ea5t sau c\u01a1n m\u01b0a b\u00e0n th\u1eafng t\u1ea1i Sochi.</h2><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">8 &ndash; Croatia \u0111\u00e3 c\u00f3 8 c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 kh\u00e1c nhau ghi b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup 2018, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 B\u1ec9 (9) l\u00e0 s\u1edf h\u1eefu nhi\u1ec1u c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 ghi b\u00e0n h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n14 &ndash; 14 trong s\u1ed1 20 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Nga ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn \u1edf s\u00e2n ch\u01a1i World Cup \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh. \u1ede gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u0103m nay, \u0111\u1ed9i ch\u1ee7 nh\u00e0 \u0111\u00e3 ph\u1ea3i nh\u1eadn 6 trong 7 b\u00e0n thua t\u1eeb nh\u1eefng t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng c\u1ed1 \u0111\u1ecbnh.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/Thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-chien-sieu-kich-tinh-Nga-vs-Croatia-hinh-anh.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>Nga vs Croatia c\u1ed1ng hi\u1ebfn cho kh\u00e1n gi\u1ea3 m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n1 &ndash; Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 trong 6 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u g\u1ea7n nh\u1ea5t \u1edf World Cup b\u01b0\u1edbc sang hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 m\u00e0 kh\u00f4ng c\u1ea7n ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft b\u1eb1ng lo\u1ea1t penalty. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn chung k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa \u0110\u1ee9c v\u00e0 Argentina n\u0103m 2014.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n2 &ndash; C\u1ea3 hai b\u00e0n th\u1eafng m\u00e0 Croatia ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua \u0111\u1ebfn t\u1eeb c\u00e1c pha \u0111\u00e1nh \u0111\u1ea7u. Theo th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea, ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 1 trong s\u1ed1 29 b\u00e0n \u1edf World Cup tr\u01b0\u1edbc&nbsp; \u0111\u00f3 c\u1ee7a Croatia \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n3 &ndash; \u0110\u00e3 c\u00f3 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u1edf s\u00e2n Fisht \u0111\u00eam qua, nhi\u1ec1u h\u01a1n b\u1ea5t k\u1ef3 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0o t\u1ea1i World Cup k\u1ec3 t\u1eeb tr\u1eadn \u0110\u1ee9c 8-0 Saudi Arabia n\u0103m 2002 (5 b\u00e0n b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width:100%; text-align: center;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Mario Fernandes\" title=\"Mario Fernandes\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/052704-3.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td style=\"text-align: center\">\r\n            <h3>C\u00f3 t\u1edbi 3 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng b\u1eb1ng \u0111\u1ea7u \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c ghi \u1edf tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1eeba qua</h3>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\n5 &ndash; Ti\u1ec1n \u0111\u1ea1o Artem Dzyuba \u0111\u00e3 in d\u1ea5u gi\u00e0y v\u00e0o 5 trong s\u1ed1 11 b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Nga \u1edf World Cup n\u0103m nay (3 b\u00e0n, 2 ki\u1ebfn t\u1ea1o).<br>\r\n<br>\r\n4 &ndash; Denis Cheryshev ghi \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c 4 b\u00e0n cho Nga \u1edf World Cup 2018. Ch\u1ec9 c\u00f3 Harry Kane c\u1ee7a \u0111\u1ed9i tuy\u1ec3n Anh l\u00e0 c\u00f3 th\u00e0nh t\u00edch t\u1ed1t h\u01a1n th\u1ebf \u1edf gi\u1ea3i \u0111\u1ea5u n\u00e0y.<br>\r\n<strong><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng tin t\u1ee9c kh\u00e1c sau tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia:<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (World Cup 2018)</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-croatia-421-190640.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Croatia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nXu\u00e2n Phong (TTVN)</strong></div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1006","checkdouble":"190656"},{"date":"06:02 08/07","title":"Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd khen \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nga","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/croatia-vao-ban-ket-dejan-lovren-khen-dt-nga.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>Dejan Lovren b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd bu\u00f4ng l\u1eddi khen ng\u1ee3i \u0111\u1ed1i th\u1ee7 Nga d\u00f9 Croatia m\u1edbi l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i gi\u00e0nh chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng \u0111\u1ec3 l\u1ecdt v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</h2><div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate2\"><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\"><img src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/993516564.jpg\" alt=\"\"></span><span href=\"/video/clip-ban-thang-nga-vs-croatia-461-190641.html\">T\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p: Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (World Cup 2018)</span><br>\r\nT\u1ed5ng h\u1ee3p di\u1ec5n bi\u1ebfn ch\u00ednh, clip b\u00e0n th\u1eafng, video highlights t\u00ecnh hu\u1ed1ng pha b\u00f3ng c\u1ee7a hi\u1ec7p 1 tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u Nga vs Croatia t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p>\u00a0</p>\r\n<h2>Dejan Lovren khen \u0110T Nga</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\"Nga \u0111\u00e3 ch\u01a1i m\u1ed9t tr\u1eadn tuy\u1ec7t hay tr\u01b0\u1edbc ch\u00fang t\u00f4i. H\u1ecd ph\u00e1 v\u1ee1 nh\u1ecbp \u0111i\u1ec7u tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u, ghi hai b\u00e0n v\u00e0 ch\u01a1i theo c\u00e1ch \u0111\u00e3 \u0111\u1ec1 ra\" - Dejan Lovren khen \u0110T Nga sau khi Croatia gi\u00e0nh v\u00e9 v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\u00a0<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren khen \u0110T Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" title=\"Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft, Dejan Lovren khen \u0110T Nga h\u00ecnh \u1ea3nh\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/croatia-vao-ban-ket-dejan-lovren-khen-dt-nga.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>Dejan Lovren khen \u0110T Nga sau tr\u1eadn t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n<br>\r\nB\u1ecb \u0111\u00e1nh gi\u00e1 th\u1ea5p h\u01a1n nh\u01b0ng \u0110T Nga b\u1ea5t ng\u1edd l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ed9i m\u1edf t\u1ec9 s\u1ed1 tr\u01b0\u1edbc v\u1edbi si\u00eau ph\u1ea9m c\u1ee7a Cheryshev. C\u00e1c h\u1ecdc tr\u00f2 c\u1ee7a HLV Cherchesov c\u0169ng thi \u0111\u1ea5u ki\u00ean c\u01b0\u1eddng trong hi\u1ec7p ph\u1ee5 v\u1edbi b\u00e0n th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Mario Fernandes. \u0110T Nga ch\u1ec9 ch\u1ecbu thua tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u khi Croatia cho th\u1ea5y b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng h\u01a1n.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n</div><mobileadv><link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Lovren cho r\u1eb1ng vi\u1ec7c Croatia \u0111i ti\u1ebfp l\u00e0 h\u1ee3p l\u00fd: \"Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i \u0111\u00e3 ch\u1ee9ng minh \u0111\u01b0\u1ee3c b\u1ea3n l\u0129nh v\u1eefng v\u00e0ng m\u1ed9t l\u1ea7n n\u1eefa. \u0110\u00f3 l\u00e0 \u0111i\u1ec1u l\u1edbn lao v\u1edbi Croatia. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i x\u1ee9ng \u0111\u00e1ng \u0111i ti\u1ebfp\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<h2 style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gi\u1edd l\u00e0 l\u00fac ngh\u0129 v\u1ec1 ng\u01b0\u1eddi Anh<br>\r\n\u00a0</h2>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110\u00e2y l\u00e0 tr\u1eadn th\u1ee9 hai li\u00ean ti\u1ebfp \u0110T Croatia ph\u1ea3i gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft tr\u00ean lo\u1ea1t lu\u00e2n l\u01b0u. Vi\u1ec7c li\u00ean t\u1ee5c ph\u1ea3i c\u0103ng s\u1ee9c khi\u1ebfn nhi\u1ec1u ng\u01b0\u1eddi lo ng\u1ea1i Croatia s\u1ebd th\u1ea5t th\u1ebf so v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh v\u1eeba c\u00f3 s\u1ee9c tr\u1ebb, v\u1eeba gi\u1ea3i quy\u1ebft Th\u1ee5y \u0110i\u1ec3n trong v\u00f2ng 90 ph\u00fat \u1edf t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n<br>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: center; width: 100%\" class=\"imagecontainer\">\r\n<table style=\"text-align: center; width:100%;\">\r\n    <tbody>\r\n        <tr style=\"width:100%;\">\r\n            <td style=\"width: 100%;\" align=\"center\"><img style=\"border: none\" alt=\"DT Croatia vao ban ket World Cup 2018.\" title=\"\u0110T Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.\" src=\"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/mobile/2018/7/8/ban-ket-wc.jpg\"></td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td>\u0110T Croatia v\u00e0o b\u00e1n k\u1ebft World Cup 2018.</td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n    </tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u0110T Croatia s\u1ebd c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 h\u1ed3i ph\u1ee5c th\u1ec3 l\u1ef1c cho c\u00e1c c\u1ea7u th\u1ee7 c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 l\u00ean k\u1ebf ho\u1ea1ch cho tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft v\u1edbi \u0110T Anh. HLV Zlatko Dalic c\u0169ng nh\u01b0 \u0111\u1ed9i tr\u01b0\u1edfng Luka Modric \u0111\u1ec1u cho r\u1eb1ng qu\u00e3ng th\u1eddi gian n\u00e0y l\u00e0 \u0111\u1ee7 \u0111\u1ec3 \"Vatreni\" chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft.<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Trong men say chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng, Lovren c\u0169ng \u0111\u1ed3ng \u00fd v\u1edbi quan \u0111i\u1ec3m n\u00e0y: \"Tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u v\u1edbi Anh s\u1ebd r\u1ea5t tuy\u1ec7t. Ch\u00fang t\u00f4i c\u00f3 b\u1ed1n ng\u00e0y \u0111\u1ec3 ngh\u1ec9 ng\u01a1i v\u00e0 chu\u1ea9n b\u1ecb cho tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u\".<br>\r\n\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">Tr\u1eadn b\u00e1n k\u1ebft gi\u1eefa Croatia vs Anh s\u1ebd di\u1ec5n ra v\u00e0o 1h00 ng\u00e0y 12/7.\r\n<h2><br>\r\nXem th\u00eam nh\u1eefng b\u00e0i vi\u1ebft kh\u00e1c tr\u00ean Bongda24h.vn v\u1ec1 \u0110T Croatia t\u1ea1i World Cup 2018:</h2>\r\n<br>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelatepannel\">\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/tin-nong-world-cup-2018/thong-ke-an-tuong-sau-tran-chien-sieu-kich-tinh-nga-vs-croatia-469-190656.html\">Th\u1ed1ng k\u00ea \u1ea5n t\u01b0\u1ee3ng sau tr\u1eadn chi\u1ebfn si\u00eau k\u1ecbch t\u00ednh Nga vs Croatia</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-croatia-noi-ve-tran-dau-voi-nga-465-190655.html\">HLV Zlatko Dalic: Nga vs Croatia kh\u00f4ng ph\u1ea3i tr\u1eadn c\u1ea7u \u0111\u1eb9p</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/hlv-nga-noi-ve-tran-thua-croatia-465-190653.html\">HLV Cherchesov t\u1ef1 h\u00e0o: Gi\u1edd th\u00ec c\u1ea3 n\u01b0\u1edbc Nga y\u00eau ch\u00fang t\u00f4i</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/toan-canh-world-cup-2018/luka-modric-noi-ve-chien-thang-cua-croatia-kich-tinh-nhu-phim-465-190652.html\">Luka Modric n\u00f3i v\u1ec1 chi\u1ebfn th\u1eafng c\u1ee7a Croatia: K\u1ecbch t\u00ednh nh\u01b0 phim</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/world-cup-2018/ket-qua-nga-vs-croatia-421-190640.html\">K\u1ebft qu\u1ea3 Nga vs Croatia tr\u1eadn \u0111\u1ea5u t\u1ee9 k\u1ebft World Cup 2018</span></div>\r\n<div class=\"articlerelate\"><span href=\"/truc-tiep-world-cup-2018/tran-dau/truc-tiep-nga-vs-croatia-463-190636.html\">Nga 2-2 (pen 3-4) Croatia (KT): G\u1ea5u Nga t\u1eeb thi\u00ean \u0111\u01b0\u1eddng xu\u1ed1ng \u0111\u1ecba ng\u1ee5c sau m\u00e0n \u0111\u1ea5u s\u00fang</span></div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\"><strong>N.D (TTVN)</strong></div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div>\r\n<div style=\"text-align: justify;\">\u00a0</div></div><advbottom>","new_url":"","id":"1005","checkdouble":"190657"},{"date":"06:31 08/07","title":"Messi v\u00e0 Ronaldo xu\u1ea5t hi\u1ec7n tr\u00ean kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i trong tr\u1eadn Nga vs Croatia","type":"B\u00f3ng \u0111\u00e1 Anh","img_url":"https://static.bongda24h.vn/medias/thumnail/2018/7/8/11.jpg","new_desc":"<link href='https://bongda24h.vn/websites/css/stylemobilev3.css?v=3' rel='stylesheet' type='text/css' /><style>body{margin:0px; padding:3px; font-size: 20px;}*{font-size:20px !important;}.articlerelatepannel { display:none; padding: 6px;  margin-top:5px; margin-bottom:5px; background-color:#f7f7f7; border:solid 1px #0cac0c}.mediaplayercontent{display:none;}h1{font-size:24px; font-weight:bold; color:black;}h2{font-weight:bold; color:black; width:100%; margin-top:5px !important;}h3{font-weight:bold; color:black;}iframe{display:none;}</style><div class='chitiet_tin'><h2>C\u00e1c c\u1ed5 \u0111\u1ed9ng vi\u00ean \u0111\u00e3 mang \u0111\u1ebfn kh\u00e1n \u0111\u00e0i s\u00e2n Fisht Olympic nh\u1eefng h\u00ecnh 